This folder contains
* master_compiled_legal_dataset.csv : Preprocessed unified dataset.
* distilled_legal_dataset.csv : Distilled dataset for Student Model Fine-Tuning.
* latest_sft_chatbot_dataset.jsonl : Chat Template - Supervised Fine-Tuning.
* distilled_state_tracker.csv : Tracking the number of rows from the preprocessed unified dataset passed to the teacher model via inference less Groq API. 
